<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Blithe" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Blithe,</orth> gay, mirthful: <cit><quote>be you b. and bonny,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 69</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 3, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.111" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 4, 111</bibl>. <cit><quote>so buxom, b. and full of face,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.111" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 4, 111</bibl></cit>. <emph>crickets sing at the oven's mouth, e'er the --er for their drouth,</emph> Per. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.0." default="NO" valid="yes">III Prol. 8</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>